OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy in the north and west overnight
OL,7,Fwith isolated light rain. Drier in
OL,8,Fsouth and east, where patchy cloud and
OL,9,Flate evening sunshine give way to
OL,10,Fclear spells overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FThe north and west remaining
OL,13,Fcloudy with a little light rain
OL,14,Fpossible. The south and east staying
OL,15,Fdry with some sunshine breaking
OL,16,Fthrough, becoming warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
