OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy few days with outbreaks of
OL,7,Flight rain and drizzle, especially in
OL,8,Fthe north and west. Drier with bright
OL,9,Fand sunny intervals in south and east.
OL,10,FWinds fresher Thursday.
